Europa League
Oleksandria-ASSE: the official teams!
AS Saint-Etienne moves to the Oleksandria pitch for the 4th day of the Europa League. Discover the official teams.
07 Nov 2019, 19:00 by Florian Sermaise
Capital displacement for ASSE! On the occasion of the fourth day of Group I Europa League, the Greens go to Ukraine to challenge Oleksandria. Two weeks after their draw at Geoffroy-Guichard (1-1), the two teams, who score in 4th and 3rd place with two points each, are indeed playing their European future tonight. Discover on this occasion the official teams of this encounter almost chopper.
The point on group I before this 4th day:

Wolfsburg - 5 pts
The Gent - 5 pts
Oleskandria - 2 pts
Saint-Etienne - 2 pts





Official teams




Mathieu Debuchy + 11 ðŸ“·Credit Photo - Icon Sport

- ASSE: Ruffier - Kolodziejczak, Perrin, Fofana, Debuchy - Aholou, Youssouf, Bouanga - Khazri, Beric, Nordin
